==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unspotted
<hw>Un*spot"ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not spotted; free
from spot or stain; especially, free from moral stain; unblemished;
immaculate; <as>as, an <ex>unspotted</ex> reputation</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*spot"ted*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsquire</ent>⟦br⟧
